MODEL WEIGHTS (NOT in this repository)
----------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository does NOT bundle voice-conversion model weights. Foundation
weights downloaded by scripts/download_weights.py at install time:

  rmvpe.onnx, rmvpe_wrapped.onnx      mirrored from huggingface.co/lj1995
                                       and huggingface.co/wok000 — see those
                                       repos for the upstream license terms
  contentvec-f.onnx                    huggingface.co/wok000/weights_gpl —
                                       upstream-licensed; see that repo
  hubert_base.pt                       huggingface.co/ddPn08 — original
                                       authors' license applies
  amitaro_v2_16k.onnx                  huggingface.co/wok000/vcclient_model
